  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In September.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In September of '42, 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there for about four weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we heard a rumor-- because after the liquidation in our home town in Poland, there  were still some few Jewish-- some Jewish population left.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my two sisters that were hidden up in the farm, they went back to our hometown.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we kept in contact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we heard in camp that was a rumor that they go and liquidate the whole town and liquidate everybody-- and a neighbor that had a home someplace and they had some valuables hidden in the attic-- and they thought if I would be there I could go and find it and maybe send it to them to the camp.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were in a different camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when I went away from the camp-- was able to run away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't that bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was not far from-- from the camp that we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a Polish family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told them if he would go with me, like buy me a ticket on the train to go to Poland-- if we-- he would get there, I would give him things from the house because what we have.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So sure enough, him and, I think, one of his daughters and he bought a ticket for them and also for me--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the two-- for this-- for the Polish-- for him and his daughter and myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to our hometown in 4 o'clock-- whatever, early in the morning and I knocked on the house and the door.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sisters, they were surprised to see me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did find something in the attic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember whether it was money or gold pieces or something like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
